  <title>Jira Connector</title>
  
  <para>The Jira Connector is an issue connector for the 
  <link xlink:href="http://www.atlassian.com/software/jira/">Jira issue and project tracking system</link>. IMPORTANT: Name of components must not contain ","</para>

  <section>
    <title>External Tool Configuration</title>
    <para>The Jira connector should work with a default Jira installation.
        However, make sure that the RPC plugin is enabled as described in the
	<link xlink:href="http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/JIRA/JIRA+XML-RPC+Overview">Jira XML-RPC Overview</link>.
    </para>
  </section>

</section>
